data.description: Welcome to a beautifully updated and unique styled Modern Country Farmhouse nestled on a generous corner lot. Featuring a charming front porch where you can relax and sip your morning coffee makes this home a true gem! Recent updates include; new tile in living area, updated kitchen, larger island, new counter tops, sink and faucet. Living area extended with a modern electrical fireplace addition. Master room closet has been extended and new toilets in  both restrooms. Full exterior makeover including the amazing porch and extended concrete pavement in backyard. BONUS room addition! Schedule a viewing and experience the charm and warmth of this beautiful home! MOTIVATED SELLER!!
